values: Today , i wake up so early again !!! Yay me !!! Don't know why i always wake up so early on weekend . Its kind of funny ... I listened to my favorite song , talked to my favorite person .... Yah ! Its life ! Love it ! Right now i feel greater than ever before ! Yay me !!!

Today i wake up so early , 'cuz i just had a wonderful dream . And its like i dont wanna lose it , so i wanna wake up even so early just to hold my dream back to me . That's a weirdest dream ever . That's funny 'cuz my character in the dream too !!!That dream never really happened in my life so far . I wish it could happen to me in the future .... Anyways , i feel so special about it . Its like i could feel , touch , act , run , cry , laugh , smile , look into someone's eyes and hug them tight !!! God ! It's like i actually played my character in that dream ...... So special !!!Love it !!!

Sometimes i wish i could go back to the past to fix all my mistakes , and i would never make any mistake again . But life is so complicated . U cant do wat u want to . U cant change wat it was . U hav nothing to do with that . Sometimes when somebody's by ur side , u dont even wanna talk to them or seeing them . But when they really leave u , u 'll realize that somewhere in ur heart hurts so bad . And u just dont wanna let them go of u . U just wanna hold them in ur arms and say that how much they mean to u . And u wanna apologize about the mean things u did to them so far . Thats exactly how i feel right now . I 'm so tired . I dont wanna let that one go of me . I'll miss that one a lot ....!!! I never know that i hav this kind of feeling ........Plz forgive me the mean things i did to u , i'll miss u a lot and never forget u .....................!!!

God ! Today i'm still sick . But atleast i feel better right now . I missed 1 phone call of H . I know H cared for me a lot everytime i get sick like this . Anyways , i'll see H on Monday . So i hav nothing to care about anymore . I just need to work extra hard right now . Hopefully , everything's gonna be okay ....

Today i'm kind of sick and tired . But its not too bad though . Maybe i'm crazy , but its like i like to be sick . 'Cuz everytime i'm sick , it brings back to me some good memories ....Right now i feel so confused about everything . I dont know why , like i got the feelings with J , but all the time i try to be really cold with J . And it makes J sad sometimes . And J thinks that i hate J ... I just act the opposite way . How stupid i am ! Anyways , everything's just confusing right now ....
